{"tid":837710,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"紅軍咁勁原來因為飲咗……","createTime":"2018-09-26T14:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T15:30:52.000Z","uid":153600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c43b6fef7476b8570b8c0801dc4d544d20f02668","tid":837710,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:40:50.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=bXVSS1kgvuXGrx8aV44%2B0Rv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=5cb951de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利物浦今季表現所向披靡，原來因為一個神秘飲品？<br />\n<br />\n德國《圖片報》爆料，指在2016年加盟的首席營養師蒙羅妮瑪，一直獲利物浦領隊高普非常信任，她最近跟前澳洲游泳冠軍禾尼基（Mark Warnecke）緊密合作，研發了一種神秘能量飲品，予紅軍球員飲用。<br />\n<br />\n這個神秘能量飲品有柑橘味及橙味，可以加速運動後的恢復。高普希望球員使用後，能夠延續開季7連勝的強勢，劍指英超冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n禾尼基在2005年以35歲之齡贏得世界游泳錦標賽男子50米蝶泳金牌，是自1971年以來最年長的世界冠軍。他在退役後創立了一家名為AMSPORT的公司，致力研究及生產提供予頂級運動員的飲品及食品。"},{"pid":"49aa72d8aa0652912ee9e05432dfa056bc2f1db0","tid":837710,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d4a3bb7023c8e35fcfe521d5e93884548341a0","tid":837710,"uid":187,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"馬馬度沙高禁藥狗"},{"pid":"1ae43021e48bd4ff967dd103e0eb7fa0eb944661","tid":837710,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7358cde50ea8783fdf9976cd39f67f1b7d89c6","tid":837710,"uid":40010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c43b6fef7476b8570b8c0801dc4d544d20f02668","tid":837710,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:40:50.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=bXVSS1kgvuXGrx8aV44%2B0Rv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=5cb951de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利物浦今季表現所向披靡，原來因為一個神秘飲品？<br />\n<br />\n德國《圖片報》爆料，指在2016年加盟的首席營養師蒙羅妮瑪，一直獲利物浦領隊高普非常信任，她最近跟前澳洲游泳冠軍禾尼基（Mark Warnecke）緊密合作，研發了一種神秘能量飲品，予紅軍球員飲用。<br />\n<br />\n這個神秘能量飲品有柑橘味及橙味，可以加速運動後的恢復。高普希望球員使用後，能夠延續開季7連勝的強勢，劍指英超冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n禾尼基在2005年以35歲之齡贏得世界游泳錦標賽男子50米蝶泳金牌，是自1971年以來最年長的世界冠軍。他在退役後創立了一家名為AMSPORT的公司，致力研究及生產提供予頂級運動員的飲品及食品。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:20:20.000Z","msg":"新奇是橙"},{"pid":"563b825e4dd5fb72981e6a554cb16cfaf6bfe896","tid":837710,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:20:31.000Z","msg":"原來沙高係比利狗教壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cf3b3ff0cb522a58633a15a316f3c127f10807","tid":837710,"uid":35070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.parknshop.com/medias/sys_master/front/prd/9042937151518.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.parknshop.com%2Fmedias%2Fsys_master%2Ffront%2Fprd%2F9042937151518.jpg&h=7d9684f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/TaZ1E5W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTaZ1E5W.png&h=7f059a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該係呢兩款<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ecd77242f2965d7ca97a3a0f7c4e8f2923ce1fc","tid":837710,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://metropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/750/pop/uploads/2017/06/05-11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmetropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F750%2Fpop%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F05-11.jpg&h=5bc50f12&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}